<ab facs="#facs_84_r3l5">Tallner <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü rede geſacʒt / vnd <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> ſpricht daʒ Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_84_r3l6"><expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vvılh<ex>elm</ex></expan> <expan>Krom<ex>er</ex></expan> etwiuil ſchuldig beleib / des er güt brief </ab>
